column5: So.. Im thinking of getting a GoPro, I see a lot of cools stuff when I'm fishing and out and about.  So I borrowed a cheaper version to try it out..  I like the fact that it catches everything, but the fish eye view makes the fish hard to see when it first hits.  The HD is nice though... however the audio makes me sound like a screeching child (LOL.. or maybe thats what I do sound like... eeeekkk.. lol)  Id like to do more videos with it for the lure store as well??
thats pretty cool T. J., your laugh is very contagious ... and the bugs in slow mo look like hummingbirds
LOL>. THats close up of a black flie.. lol.. looks as big as a dragon fly... I gotta say.. I can't remember a weekend where the bugs have been worse in recent memory...
You do sound like a school girl! I had to take a second look to make sure that the youtube link wasn't a NKOTB sighting! HH

holly bugs!  Those go-pros are awesome.  We where riding single track last weekend, and got a chance to try one out as well.  Very cool!  I have also heard really good things about the Contour camera.  I think that is what the dude on Uncut Angling always has hanging off the side of his melon.  You might want to check them out too.  No case needed, they are waterproof out of the box.  A little less bulky I think.  http://store.contour.com/
I,ll get you my pretty,hehehehehehehe LMAO   That was cool on the second hit.  Nice to see they didnt kick yer beer over. Nice side step.LOL
Tj the hero 3 cameras are much better they also have a new housing that takes the fish eye away. Great first vid I can not wait for the ones when your excited
I loved it!!!  Everything was cool about that (even you laughing)
Thanks guys, I should get some more interesting stuff on the trip north..
Beauty spot on the river there for Jiggy. You had me laughing too T.J.
No, that's what you sound like normally  Really cool video TJ!
For any of your fisherman that have Go-Pro's, Please shoot me PM's with your YouTube links and I'll add it to my new website http://www.goproangling.com.
"Oh it's all gone bad"  lol  great video!!
